Use this template to avoid producing a [[help:self link|self link]].

== 使用方法 ==
<code>{{tlp|Link if not current|Article}}</code> produces
* a list item linking to [[Article]] if the current page's title is not <code>Article</code>,
* nothing if it is.

=== 参数 ===
*Parameter 1 is necessary, as it is the link.
*Parameter 2 is optional, and it is the text that is displayed over the link. If parameter 2 doesn't exist, it defaults to parameter 1.

== 另见 ==
* {{tl|No selflink}} – always outputs the text (either linked or not) and NOT embedded in a list item
* {{tl|Link if exists}}
* {{tl|Link if equal}}

